#. module: cyllo_field_service
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_field_service.mail_template_field_service_request_deadline
msgid ""
"<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"padding-top: 16px; background-color: #F1F1F1; font-family:Verdana, Arial,sans-serif; color: #454748;border-collapse:separate;\">\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <td align=\"center\">\n"
"                        <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"590\" style=\"padding: 16px; background-color: white; color: #454748; border-collapse:separate;  margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n"
"                            <tbody>\n"
"                                <!-- CONTENT -->\n"
"                                <tr>\n"
"                                    <td align=\"center\" style=\"min-width: 590px;\">\n"
"                                        <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"590\" style=\"min-width: 590px; background-color: white; padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px; border-collapse:separate;\">\n"
"                                            <tr>\n"
"                                                <td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"                                                    <div>\n"
"                                                        Dear\n"
"                                                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('name')\"></t>\n"
"                                                        ,\n"
"                                                        <br>\n"
"                                                        <br>\n"
"                                                        This is a friendly reminder that your service request (Reference: <t t-out=\"object.name\"></t>) is nearing its deadline. The service is scheduled to be completed by <t t-out=\"object.date_deadline.date()\"></t>,\n"
"                                                        Please ensure that all necessary preparations are in place to facilitate a smooth and timely resolution.\n"
"                                                    </div>\n"
"                                                </td>\n"
"                                            </tr>\n"
"                                        </table>\n"
"                                    </td>\n"
"                                </tr>\n"
"                            </tbody>\n"
"                        </table>\n"
"                    </td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"            </table>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<tablica Border = \"0\" CellPadding = \"0\" CellSpacing = \"0\" Style = \"Padding-TOP: 16PX; pozadinsko-boj: #F1F1F1; FONT-FONT: VERDANA, ARIAL, SANS-SERIF; BOJA: #454748;granični kolaps: odvojeno; \">\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td poravnanje = \"središte\">\n"
"<tablica Border = \"0\" CellPadding = \"0\" CellSpacing = \"0\" WIDTH = \"590\" Style = \"Padding: 16px; Background Color: White; Color: #454748; Border-Collapse: Odvojeno;20px; \">\n"
"<TBody>\n"
"<!-Sadržaj->\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td elagn = \"centra\" stil = \"min-širina: 590px;\">\n"
"<tablica Border = \"0\" CellPadding = \"0\" CellSpacing = \"0\" WIDTH = \"590\" Style = \"Min-širina: 590px; Backgrour-Color: White; Padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px; granična kovapsa: odvojeno;\">\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td valign = \"top\" stil = \"font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"<IV>\n"
"Dragi\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('name')\"> </t>\n"
",,\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ovo je prijateljski podsjetnik da se vaš zahtjev za uslugu (referenca: <t t-out = \"objekt.name\"> </t>) bliži roku.Usluga bi trebala biti dovršena <t t-out = \"Object.Date_Deadline.Date ()\"> </t>,\n"
"Molimo osigurajte da su sve potrebne pripreme za olakšavanje glatke i pravovremene rezolucije.\n"
